    java.lang.Cloneable, Changeable, Debuggable, DebugListener, Derivable, IconAttribute, ModelErrorHandler, MoMLExportable, Moveable, Nameable, ValueListener
    public class ActorNameIcon
extends BoxedValueIcon
    An icon that displays the parameter _displayedName. This differs from BoxedValueIcon in that it uses the _displayedName parameter and hides the name of the container.
